com.polarion.alm.builder.model

Interface IBuild

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAdaptable, IChangeListener, IHasValues, IPObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ITrackerBuild

    public interface IBuild
extends IPObject
    Build representation.

    Object id is unique within one IBuildArtifact.getGroupEntity() and is equal to getBuildStamp().

    Author:
    Stepan Roh, Polarion Software

      • getAuthor

        IUser getAuthor()
        User who run this build/calculation.

        More specifically this is the user whose Subject was used when master build/calculation job was spawned.

        In case there is no Polarion user corresponding to caller, default or synthetic user is supplied.

        Returns:
        user (not null)

      • getLogFiles

        java.util.Collection getLogFiles()
        All available log files associated with this build stored in the IBuilderService.getBuildInformationRepository().

        This will typically be available only after build finished and log files were transferred to BIR.

        It is possible that returned log files do not exist in the time of calling.

        For list of log files available during whole job lifecycle see method ILogger.getLogFiles() of interface ILogger retrievable from IJobUnit.getLogger() of associated IJob. Note that these two sets of log files may be different (there may be additional log files available from one or the other).

        As long as job is associated with this build, use ILogger.getLogEvents() instead of log files (either retrieved from job or from this method).

        Locations are relative to getBIRLocation().

        Returns:
        Collection of ILocations (not null)

      • getBuildEvents

        @NotNull
IBuildEvents getBuildEvents()
        Gathered build events.

        Typically based on log (but filtered to contain only normal and fatal errors). The returned value should not be modified by clients outside of the builds framework.

        Returns:
        IBuildEvents (not null)

      • getDeployedArtifacts

        java.util.Collection getDeployedArtifacts()
        Information about artifacts deployed to BIR during the build.

        Is empty for plain calculations. Is filled after the build has finished.

        Returns:
        Collection of IBuildDeploymentArtifacts (not null)

      • getBuildTestResults

        @Nullable
IBuildTestResults getBuildTestResults()
        Test results, filled after the build has finished.

        Is null for plain calculations, or before the build has finished.

        Returns:
        IBuildTestResults or null
